{
  "texts": [
    "In most scenarios, the collaboration of various techniques within the FL framework is necessary.",
    "For instance, knowledge distillation shows promising potential in overcoming many challenges through the transfer of abstract knowledge, such as addressing heterogeneity and facilitating multi-task learning.",
    "Additionally, exploring the application of transfer learning for knowledge reuse under federated learning is meaningful.",
    "This approach can improve data utilization and effectively reduce repeated training in federated scenarios with label scarcity or reinforcement learning.",
    "Therefore, we suggest studying how multiple federated learning paradigms can work together to address both existing and new challenges."
  ]
}